example.property_title: Rustic-Chic Villa with a Courtyard Pool, Surrounded by Palms
example.property_overview: Dive in from the living room, then float in a COURTYARD PRIVATE POOL. The rugged charm of exposed plaster walls and a flagstone floor was inspired by Portuguese styling, while colorful tiled meeting nooks and cute chalk murals showcase local creativity. Our MINIMALIST designed villa has a simple, straightforward, efficient plan layout with stacked volumes of spaces. Simple forms, open floor plans, minimal interior walls, modest storage areas, and an emphasis on views and daylight are defining characteristics of this minimalist villa.
